{"tid":1526342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Popo就好似二戰時既日本","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T06:11:13.000Z","uid":131875,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"51fd92bb07ce8f7967aa98f6ea97c017aa23e9b5","tid":1526342,"uid":131875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:30:52.000Z","msg":"take過elective日本文化<br />\n唔知我講得啱唔啱<br />\n日本文化入面有樣野叫集團意識<br />\n導致佢地極度團結而排外<br />\n個人意志已經冇左<br />\n二戰時有好多冇人性既行為只要一個人做左<br />\n就大家都要一齊做<br />\n唔做既話就當係敵人<br />\n覺得同而家既popo好似<br />\n如果係咁<br />\n警局內新屋嶺內真係咩都有可能發生"},{"pid":"9bfde68277791734c872354bc76e38a42ad7de53","tid":1526342,"uid":196552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"配合中國既軍國主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6758609a7b488ecdfa4f01d0103a8dd07413c80e","tid":1526342,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"所以撐警嘅唔再係藍絲，係港奸"},{"pid":"daa979d29e32a20de2cea6b74d33cbe90d642ca9","tid":1526342,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:34:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e12324a077c808e840f3509091fb53b200bd2307","tid":1526342,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"149fc2a0f85720316b019856c03b144444dfbc13","tid":1526342,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7004415b7d877e37c2e11e0a4db44ffc9d0702","tid":1526342,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係好嬲"},{"pid":"c7d9d67ff633ff0b5e5079bbb5309cab3c6a6335